Interface RulePipelineState

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavacPipelineState

    public interface RulePipelineState
extends AutoCloseable
    When SupportsPipelining rules are built locally, each is given an instance of a class that implements this interface. The rules in the pipeline share build state through that object.
